	<message key="plugins.generic.reviewerCertificate.emailCertificate.defaultSubject">Acknowledgement of your review for {{$journalName}}</message>
	<message key="plugins.generic.reviewerCertificate.emailCertificate.defaultBody">Dear {{$reviewerName}},

We are immensely grateful for your efforts and time devoted to reviewing the manuscript entitled "{{$submissionTitle}}" submitted to {{$journalName}}. Your meticulous and insightful evaluation has provided valuable feedback that has helped the authors improve their work and advance their research endeavors.

Your contribution to maintaining the quality of the articles published in our journal is highly appreciated. We understand that reviewing manuscripts is a demanding task, and we acknowledge the effort you put into thoroughly analyzing the submission and providing constructive criticism to the authors.

To show our appreciation for your hard work, we would like to kindly ask you to forward this letter to reviews@webofscience.com. Please note that in accordance with our editorial policy, the content of the review will remain confidential and will not be displayed on Web of Science.

Your reviewer certificate is attached to this letter.

Once again, we extend our gratitude for your commitment to the advancement of research in your field. We hope to continue collaborating with you in the future.

Best regards,

{{$editorName}}
{{$journalName}}</message>
